      <title>摩根大通寻求合作伙伴，私人债务接近 30 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/jpmorgan-nears-3-billion-for-private-debt-in-hunt-for-partners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通据知情人士透露，该公司正在洽谈获得 25 亿至 30 亿美元的第三方承诺，以发展其私人信贷战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/jpmorgan-nears-3-billion-for-private-debt-in-hunt-for-partners</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 20:51:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗是考虑收购红石的私募股权公司之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/apollo-is-among-private-equity-firms-mulling-a-redstone-buyout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司(Apollo Global Management Inc.)正在考虑向国家娱乐公司(National Amusements Inc.)提出收购要约，该公司是红石家族公司，控制着电影电视巨头派拉蒙全球公司(Paramount Global)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/apollo-is-among-private-equity-firms-mulling-a-redstone-buyout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 20:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大多数未能支付学生贷款的美国人表示他们无力承担</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/most-student-loan-non-payers-say-they-can-t-afford-to-keep-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费城联邦储备银行的最新研究显示，自 10 月份重启以来未能支付学生贷款账单的美国人中有一半以上表示，主要原因是无力支付。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/most-student-loan-non-payers-say-they-can-t-afford-to-keep-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 17:51:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citadel 与对冲基金同行一起削减因指数变化而进行的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/citadel-joins-peers-cutting-back-trading-on-index-changes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Citadel 已经调整了指数再平衡策略，加入了一系列对冲基金同行的行列，他们正在削减曾经是最可靠的交易之一，但近年来变得充满挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/citadel-joins-peers-cutting-back-trading-on-index-changes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jan 2024 15:20:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国现房销售下降，创下 1995 年以来最差年份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/us-existing-home-sales-decline-to-cap-worst-year-since-1995</link>
      <description><![CDATA[12 月份美国二手房销量下降，成为近三十年来房地产市场最糟糕的一年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/us-existing-home-sales-decline-to-cap-worst-year-since-1995</guid>
